It was a pleasure to host the new USAID Head of Mission, Nancy Eslick, and other USAID team members on the 28th of October to Save the Children office, to provide a briefing about FCF | REACT. Nancy had the opportunity to meet a number of the Save the Children team, and a great discussion was held on the importance of family-based care for children in Cambodia. We look forward to continued close collaboration with Nancy and the USAID team.

